message.body: Hi Juls! Sorry I didn't see your msg until this morning. We're going to a baby car seat inspection thing at 9 am. I'm free all day after that, but Jason is helping a friend move. Would you like to do lunch?
1 is perfect! What do you feel like? Noodles? Panera? I'm down for whatever.
Let's say noodles at 1. Bonus: my mom has noodles coupons so I think we get free drinks!! It'll be a thrill!
